name: Jmbde-xcode
tagline: A little BDE Tool with Xcode
body:
### Welcome to jmbde-Xcode Pages.
A tool for data acquisition

version 0.1

by Jürgen Mülbert

The JMBDE program is used to record employees, computers, printers, phones and copiers. This of course includes the software, the computer and the accounts of the employees.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
